room_title: Escape room "Flashback to the 80's!" by Dare Escape Rooms in Eugene
room_address: 2160 W 11th Ave Suite I Eugene, OR 97402
room_description: A prominent 80's film director Hugh Johns is missing his lucky director's clapboard. It has been stolen by a competing director! His nemesis has gone back in time and hid the clapboard somewhere in an 80's movie prop studio. When you flashback to the 80's, be sure to come in your best 80's attire. Can you find the clapboard and make your way back from this time-traveling adventure?
